---
title: Cornmeal-Crusted Tilapia and Shrimp with DIY Tartar Sauce and Coleslaw
description: The classic fish-n-chips gets a makeover! Fresh white fish is topped with cornmeal and baked. Served with shrimp, slaw, roasted potatoes and DIY tartar sauce, this dinner is a hit!
